  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test the effect of an implanted device that stimulates the
      stomach to help obese patients lose weight.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to evaluate efficacy and safety of the IGS system in a
      population of patients with a BMI between 35 and 55 kg/m2.

      SHAPE was a randomized, placebo-controlled, double-blind, multi-center pivotal study in which
      all subjects were implanted with the IGS system.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
